ArduinoLib :

I. Prerequisies:

sudo apt-get install cmake
sudo apt-get install gcc-avr binutils-avr avr-libc


II. Build :

In order for the shell script build.sh to run properly you need to:

- define and export ARDUINO_INSTALL (export ARDUINO_INSTALL="~/Dev/ArduinoLib/install")
- define and export ARDUINO_INCLUDE (export ARDUINO_INCLUDE="~/Dev/ArduinoLib/install/include/Arduino")
- define and export ARDUINO_LIB (export ARDUINO_LIB="~/Dev/ArduinoLib/install/lib/static/")
 
- run the script from where it is (and not from an other directory)

Run:

./build.sh